Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,天神很快就要降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這可能是人作為種群的極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有勇者大人成為了御姿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能達成神婚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,讓神樹大人獲得新的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,又要強迫她們做殘酷的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是無力的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,只能聆聽聲音和祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是被選中之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這是榮譽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有其他方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這是保護神性較低的民眾的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,最後的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大家化為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,被拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這能說是活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,說話謹慎點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不是身為人的我們能對抗的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,交給勇者大人和神樹大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不會被勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妨礙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,儀式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的話 和天神的攻擊一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就無法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我們的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就算人世結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,人的靈魂會和地神一起化為永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,和神樹大人同在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,和神樹大人同在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,靈魂口牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,人類的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,知道厲害了嗎 天神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來 小鷲她們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經是累贅了 扔下我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼呢 夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事情 絕對不允許
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,和姐姐她們會合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,奪回友奈 大家一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 道路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,由我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,來劈開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要去到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要是再失去什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒辦法原諒我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以拜託了 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,樹 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不作惡就沒辦法存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不承認是神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有過好多的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,為了國家 犧牲也是無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信那是崇高的 正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛著這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,憑精靈的力量能回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,回家吧 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,做到這個程度 都不想交出她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 我這就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 我… 我不做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,世界會消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想失去友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,必須由我去做 只有我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這一點也不像東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明是把國家放在第一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事 是必須有人去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再有重要之人被奪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那種浮於表面的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼一直都要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因為只要我忍耐 就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,說真話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕就說害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我你不願意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就叫我救你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可是不能說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可是那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不想和大家分別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:09:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們 明明那麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是任務所以沒辦法 這種話是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,想一直和大家在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 伸出手來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這 居然不惜做到這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這 居然不惜做到這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們對這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,也是感謝的 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:11:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不惜捨棄人身 捨棄朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,也要得到的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那種世界 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,人 有形形色色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此 真的想要救人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你能相信人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要走作為人的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是 我才對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,對東鄉做了過分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 世界要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,世界要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這不怪友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果世界要這樣結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,牛鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要作為人類戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者 不屈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,無論多少次都會站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,為了友奈的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只要去做 多半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,會有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,FIGHT！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是毅力！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,火焰…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這 和平時不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,牛鬼 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,還存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了？ 散華？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是平時的 天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 友奈 不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,烙印消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,還活著呢 和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:50.45,Top,,0,0,0,,所以才能努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這是最後的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.45,0:23:51.74,Top,,0,0,0,,沒辦法祈禱也沒辦法接受懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:52.16,Top,,0,0,0,,樹 加油
Comment: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:53.24,Top,,0,0,0,,我一直都在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:53.50,Top,,0,0,0,,你太極端了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我永遠都在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.50,0:23:54.54,Top,,0,0,0,,今後要更加做好勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是聯繫著未來之人的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:23:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,致明日的勇者
